      First Kaplan Fellowship
     </h4>
     <div class="content">
      <p>
       UCLA alumnus Richard Kaplan, founder of the research and development company Ultramet, has generously donated funding to establish The Kaplan Pioneer Graduate Award. The first winner is Mr. Krishna Choudhary for his work on neuronal mechanics associated with locating the individual in space and time.
